{"tid":820643,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)養鬼食人/針頭鬼1-3","createTime":"2018-09-15T14:04:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-15T17:31:52.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1bcef9bc8aef744d114bb42294a88bd433082a0a","tid":820643,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:04:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=1cbee0c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=8a81ad5a\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有OKRU睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=e7bab6c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵 <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/7/7b/Hellraiser_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F7%2F7b%2FHellraiser_Poster.jpg&h=4f1a1b88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.賴瑞與第二任妻子茱莉亞(Julia)搬入新家，然而賴瑞卻不知道茱莉亞早與自己的兄弟法蘭克有染，茱莉亞得知情人法蘭克被一個神秘的魔盒殺死，需要人血獻祭才能復活，便開始勾引獵殺無辜的男人，另一方面，賴瑞的女兒克莉絲汀(Kirsty)撿到了魔盒，不小心釋放出「針頭」等地獄修道士們......<br />\n<br />\n2.克莉絲汀進了精神病院，遇到了沉迷於邪術研究的查納德醫生，他不但以人血將邪惡的茱莉亞復活，還利用自閉症女孩蒂芬妮解開魔盒，開啟地獄之門，闖入地獄世界的克莉絲汀與蒂芬妮等人能全身而退嗎.....?<br />\n<br />\n3.女記者喬伊目賭一樁鐵鍊殺人慘案，決心要查出真相，而調查途中又牽扯出了針頭鬼欲復活並且將人間化為地獄的陰謀，眼看針頭大開殺戒，喬伊能阻止他嗎?而不斷出現在喬伊夢中的神秘男子艾略特．史賓賽將會是打敗針頭的關鍵...?<br />\n<br />\n10 20PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f96fadcf\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=S0akONC3rN1kuGo3BMaDKpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=4f56d772\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac00258c38767520e823b448541113683a7569a","tid":820643,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d87d7bfc770094242199d8ead566c98e2aafe406","tid":820643,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T14:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcccf9495ccc4b86fb4ec403cd87a54ef3d2b093","tid":820643,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T16:23:24.000Z","msg":"<